com.ephox.version

Interface VersionManager


  • public interface VersionManager
    A set of APIs to assist in determining the platform EditLive! is running on. Instance available via ELJBean.getVersionManager().
    Since:
    7.5

      • isVersionRightForPlugin

        boolean isVersionRightForPlugin(String minimumVersionRequiredForPlugin,
                              String pluginName)
        Allows plugins to specify a minimum version of EditLive! they support, and the editor will return true if the plugin should attempt to load
        Parameters:
        minimumVersionRequiredForPlugin - minimum version as string (e.g. "9.0")
        pluginName - plugin name
        Returns:
        is plugin supported on the current version of EditLive?
        See Also:
        SafeLoadingPlugin
